name: Power Kick (A Love You Can't Deny)
description: Production: @requisit_fa Lyrics + Vocals: @ccffdead Lyrics: Okay, I admit it / I don’t know what’s a bit and what’s my personality anymore / At least I’m not a bore / At least I’m your favorite whore next door / I think you love that I’m a chore / When you see me / I know your feet will hit the / Floor / Power Kick, move them hips / I wanna see your body shake / Don’t even think or hesitate / The rhythm will keep us sane / Through these starlights and champagne / Pray to the Dj / He might save a life tonight / Our love will never die, alright? / This dance floor without you? / That’s a scary sight / It’s not worth it / I can’t lie / Like a MAC truck / Faced a couple of blunts / At the party, I see you / That’s good luck / Any minute with you / I’m starstruck / My / words I mutter / My words I stutter / My words? / They falter / But on that dance floor you’ll see / As fate would have it be / When that beat go off / These Power Kicks will show you’ll see / A love you can’t deny baby / It’s 2 am, and it’s the end of the night / When we're both lit by starlight / Decompress in the cold / And fit your favorite jacket’s mold / I’ll have to ask / Can I take you home?
